    title="Earnings Call Analyser"
    subtitle="Does the way executives answer analysts predict the next quarter's returns?"
    description="A PyTorch + FinBERT pipeline testing Chiang et al. 2025 on Q&A alignment as an equity signal. Architecture is complete; the next step is a labelled training set."
    status="Field Note · 04"
    repo="https://github.com/jevancousins/earnings-call-analyser"
    meta={[
      { label: 'Status', value: 'Proof of concept' },
      { label: 'Started', value: 'Q1 2026' },
      { label: 'Stack', value: 'PyTorch · FinBERT · K8s' },
      { label: 'Embedding', value: '768-dim FinBERT' },
